746
00:33:38,019 --> 00:33:38,720
[SPEAKER_01] ako sam u Livnu,

747
00:33:38,720 --> 00:33:39,859
[SPEAKER_01] to mu se stavi preze mene,

748
00:33:39,859 --> 00:33:41,240
[SPEAKER_01] to je isto potpuno.

749
00:33:41,240 --> 00:33:43,019
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo porijeklom ramljani,

750
00:33:43,019 --> 00:33:44,420
[SPEAKER_01] Sinjen, Cetinski kraj,

751
00:33:44,420 --> 00:33:46,079
[SPEAKER_01] gospod Milosti Ramska,

752
00:33:46,079 --> 00:33:47,339
[SPEAKER_01] gospod Sinska,

753
00:33:47,339 --> 00:33:48,299
[SPEAKER_01] znači prema,

754
00:33:48,299 --> 00:33:49,240
[SPEAKER_01] to mi nije,

755
00:33:49,240 --> 00:33:49,619
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

756
00:33:49,619 --> 00:33:50,940
[SPEAKER_01] ona šala da smo ugrali,

757
00:33:50,940 --> 00:33:51,160
[SPEAKER_01] ne,

758
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:52,980
[SPEAKER_01] to je bio zbijeg pred Turcima,

759
00:33:52,980 --> 00:33:54,380
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je propao u Učkovići,

760
00:33:54,380 --> 00:33:54,960
[SPEAKER_01] znači ramljani.

761
00:33:54,960 --> 00:33:56,579
[SPEAKER_01] To ćemo neki drugi potkaz.

762
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:57,779
[SPEAKER_01] Mene, malo šale,

763
00:33:57,779 --> 00:33:58,759
[SPEAKER_01] da...

764
00:33:58,759 --> 00:34:00,259
[SPEAKER_01] Nisamo porijeklom,

765
00:34:00,259 --> 00:34:02,039
[SPEAKER_01] znači Cetinski kraj iz rame.

766
00:34:02,039 --> 00:34:04,400
[SPEAKER_01] Nisamo isti narod,

767
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:05,440
[SPEAKER_01] iz ta krv.

768
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:08,219
[SPEAKER_01] Kad neko kaže,

769
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:11,179
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam bio u Bosni godinu,

770
00:34:11,179 --> 00:34:12,340
[SPEAKER_01] znači u ratu.

771
00:34:12,340 --> 00:34:13,440
[SPEAKER_01] Osobno.

772
00:34:13,440 --> 00:34:14,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam ponosan.

773
00:34:14,780 --> 00:34:16,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam bio nad Banjelukom.

774
00:34:16,659 --> 00:34:19,239
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim,

775
00:34:19,239 --> 00:34:20,559
[SPEAKER_01] tako su bižali,

776
00:34:20,559 --> 00:34:21,440
[SPEAKER_01] Dodeg i Vučići,

777
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,900
[SPEAKER_01] i ono saka veći kako se bače.

778
00:34:22,900 --> 00:34:23,619
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim,

779
00:34:23,619 --> 00:34:24,219
[SPEAKER_01] dođe čovku,

780
00:34:24,219 --> 00:34:24,360
[SPEAKER_01] jel?

781
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:25,380
[SPEAKER_01] Prema tome,

782
00:34:25,380 --> 00:34:27,559
[SPEAKER_01] tu ima dobru politiku,

783
00:34:27,559 --> 00:34:29,219
[SPEAKER_01] ja moram prezentujem dobru,

784
00:34:29,219 --> 00:34:29,559
[SPEAKER_01] kao,

785
00:34:29,559 --> 00:34:31,079
[SPEAKER_01] govorim kao presnik.

786
00:34:31,079 --> 00:34:31,780
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

787
00:34:31,780 --> 00:34:32,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet,

788
00:34:32,420 --> 00:34:33,980
[SPEAKER_00] veliki dio naroda ne osjeća to,

789
00:34:33,980 --> 00:34:35,059
[SPEAKER_00] što sada govorite.

790
00:34:35,059 --> 00:34:36,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam,

791
00:34:36,099 --> 00:34:37,219
[SPEAKER_01] zbog čega ne osjeća.

792
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:39,119
[SPEAKER_01] Zoran Milanović je dio,

793
00:34:39,119 --> 00:34:41,500
[SPEAKER_01] jedan bio bitan sigurnosti,

794
00:34:41,500 --> 00:34:43,320
[SPEAKER_01] je diplomatski diplomacija.

795
00:34:43,320 --> 00:34:45,860
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo dva čovuka na čelu državi,

796
00:34:45,860 --> 00:34:48,800
[SPEAKER_01] to je Zrinjevačku bojnu,

797
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:50,360
[SPEAKER_01] ja je voli nazvat Krobasan bojnu.

798
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:54,239
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo Plenkovića i Milanovića,

799
00:34:54,239 --> 00:34:58,679
[SPEAKER_01] koji su sa Zrinjevca ponikli iz diplomacije,

800
00:34:58,679 --> 00:35:00,380
[SPEAKER_01] a onda su i diplomaciju ništa,

801
00:35:00,380 --> 00:35:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne samo on,

802
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:03,460
[SPEAKER_01] nego cijela struktura upravljačka

803
00:35:03,460 --> 00:35:04,880
[SPEAKER_01] i Jan Troković,

804
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:06,860
[SPEAKER_01] i Milanović,

805
00:35:07,079 --> 00:35:07,920
[SPEAKER_01] i Plenkoviću,

806
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:08,679
[SPEAKER_01] i Kolinda,

807
00:35:08,679 --> 00:35:09,500
[SPEAKER_01] pretkonca,

808
00:35:09,500 --> 00:35:10,059
[SPEAKER_01] sve je to,

809
00:35:10,059 --> 00:35:11,860
[SPEAKER_01] Gorgrančeva škola,

810
00:35:11,860 --> 00:35:13,539
[SPEAKER_01] tu je Budimir Lončar bio,

811
00:35:13,539 --> 00:35:14,639
[SPEAKER_01] tata Matečov,

812
00:35:14,639 --> 00:35:16,519
[SPEAKER_01] koji je glavni za embargo,

813
00:35:16,519 --> 00:35:17,480
[SPEAKER_01] da se uvede Hrvatsko,

814
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:19,219
[SPEAKER_01] je vodio cilu tu priču,

815
00:35:19,219 --> 00:35:20,940
[SPEAKER_01] sad se da nje suzeliju.

816
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ima on te neke poteze,

817
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:23,559
[SPEAKER_01] međutim,

818
00:35:23,559 --> 00:35:26,099
[SPEAKER_01] meni odmah ne prihvatili poteze,

819
00:35:26,099 --> 00:35:27,340
[SPEAKER_01] ako čovuka je da tribao,

820
00:35:27,340 --> 00:35:28,980
[SPEAKER_01] sloboditi Mustače Perkovića,

821
00:35:29,420 --> 00:35:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] ljude,

822
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:32,199
[SPEAKER_01] koji su naređivali da nekoga ubiju s sikerom,

823
00:35:32,199 --> 00:35:33,980
[SPEAKER_01] joj rekao ćeo bilo s sikerom,

824
00:35:33,980 --> 00:35:35,079
[SPEAKER_01] da ih se pomilju,

825
00:35:35,079 --> 00:35:36,280
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam prvi bio kričan,

826
00:35:36,280 --> 00:35:39,300
[SPEAKER_01] da se obezređuju insigne Dominskog rata,

827
00:35:39,940 --> 00:35:42,099
[SPEAKER_01] a ti su bristeli po Zrinjevci i o Krovasani.

828
00:35:42,099 --> 00:35:44,659
[SPEAKER_01] On se sa hosom domstavom izrugio,

829
00:35:44,659 --> 00:35:47,079
[SPEAKER_01] s insignem hospo Osreba,

830
00:35:47,079 --> 00:35:49,159
[SPEAKER_01] koja je brana Hrvatsko od Vukovar do Dubrovnika,

831
00:35:49,159 --> 00:35:50,260
[SPEAKER_01] uluzimo sad to vrijeme,

832
00:35:50,260 --> 00:35:54,559
[SPEAKER_01] u sami tjedan sjećanja na žrtu Vukovara,

833
00:35:54,559 --> 00:35:56,280
[SPEAKER_01] herojsku obronu grada Vukovara.

834
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:59,300
[SPEAKER_01] Kroma tome, sigurnost je sve,

835
00:35:59,300 --> 00:36:00,840
[SPEAKER_01] sigurnost je vrijednost,

836
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:03,380
[SPEAKER_01] najveća vrijednost i temelj je domovinski rat.

837
00:36:03,380 --> 00:36:05,219
[SPEAKER_01] Danas sam je rekao,

838
00:36:05,219 --> 00:36:07,099
[SPEAKER_01] će biti moj prvi potiz za oto išponoviti,

839
00:36:07,880 --> 00:36:10,480
[SPEAKER_01] da ću vrhovni zapovjednik,

840
00:36:10,480 --> 00:36:11,800
[SPEAKER_01] da sam ja vrhovni zapovjednik,

841
00:36:11,800 --> 00:36:15,340
[SPEAKER_01] bio bi prvi potiz odmah vratiti,

842
00:36:15,340 --> 00:36:16,760
[SPEAKER_01] to jest odruzjeto,

843
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] heroju, junaku Dominskog rata Mirku Norca.

844
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:24,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ne može se toliko obezvrijediti uloga ljudi,

845
00:36:24,039 --> 00:36:25,340
[SPEAKER_01] koji su kao mladiće,

846
00:36:25,340 --> 00:36:27,539
[SPEAKER_01] preuzjeli ulogu zapovjedanja

847
00:36:27,539 --> 00:36:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] i zaustavljanja jedne od najčijih vojski Evropi.

848
00:36:31,039 --> 00:36:33,840
[SPEAKER_01] Jugoslavijanske narodne armije,

849
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:35,099
[SPEAKER_01] zajedno s četnih suma.

850
00:36:35,099 --> 00:36:37,400
[SPEAKER_01] I sad ćemo mi obezvrijediti tog čovka,

851
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] pa nije on bio na pikniku.

852
00:36:38,500 --> 00:36:39,800
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, da, ja ne,

853
00:36:39,800 --> 00:36:41,280
[SPEAKER_01] podržaju nikakve zločine ono.

854
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:43,159
[SPEAKER_01] Nije to bio piknik na Zrinjevcu.

855
00:36:43,159 --> 00:36:46,300
[SPEAKER_01] Nije Plešnjak negdje odan po Zagrebi,

856
00:36:46,300 --> 00:36:47,340
[SPEAKER_01] su Plenković, ne znam,

857
00:36:47,340 --> 00:36:49,519
[SPEAKER_01] Milanović, Androković,

858
00:36:49,519 --> 00:36:51,320
[SPEAKER_01] Plesali, nemam pojma ko s njima.

859
00:36:51,320 --> 00:36:54,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je bilo ostat miljanči prijatelj Plenkoviće.

860
00:36:54,400 --> 00:36:56,460
[SPEAKER_01] To je sve i sad družbe.

861
00:36:56,460 --> 00:36:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] I on sve dječačko prijatelstvo,

862
00:36:58,960 --> 00:37:01,219
[SPEAKER_01] su stvorili zbog ambicijalne prijatelstvo

863
00:37:01,219 --> 00:37:03,440
[SPEAKER_01] i čak su uništili diplomaciju.

864
00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:04,320
[SPEAKER_01] Tri godine.

865
00:37:04,320 --> 00:37:08,219
[SPEAKER_01] Nije imenovalo velopostanice.

866
00:37:08,219 --> 00:37:10,639
[SPEAKER_01] Nisu razriješeni ti imenovali.

867
00:37:10,639 --> 00:37:11,019
[SPEAKER_01] Isti.

868
00:37:11,019 --> 00:37:12,760
[SPEAKER_01] Tri godine,

869
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:14,679
[SPEAKER_01] Vijeće za obranu se nije sastalo.

870
00:37:14,679 --> 00:37:16,619
[SPEAKER_01] I Vijeće za nacionalnu sigurnost.

871
00:37:17,099 --> 00:37:18,800
[SPEAKER_01] A znate u kakvim vremenima živimo.

872
00:37:18,800 --> 00:37:20,059
[SPEAKER_01] Prema tome,

873
00:37:20,059 --> 00:37:21,340
[SPEAKER_01] na tome trija puno rata,

874
00:37:21,340 --> 00:37:23,039
[SPEAKER_01] a ja kao vrhovni zapojednik

875
00:37:23,039 --> 00:37:23,920
[SPEAKER_01] od svih kada zata

876
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] sam bio najdružaj vojnik,

877
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:28,199
[SPEAKER_01] profesorne vojnik, častnik sam

878
00:37:28,199 --> 00:37:29,880
[SPEAKER_01] i zasiguro svih njima,

879
00:37:29,880 --> 00:37:30,719
[SPEAKER_01] što oni god rekli.

880
00:37:30,719 --> 00:37:32,719
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo ono diplomacije,

881
00:37:32,719 --> 00:37:33,380
[SPEAKER_01] bilo ono ovo,

882
00:37:33,380 --> 00:37:34,019
[SPEAKER_01] bilo ono,

883
00:37:34,019 --> 00:37:35,760
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam osječizme.

884
00:37:35,760 --> 00:37:36,840
[SPEAKER_01] Moje soborce.

885
00:37:36,840 --> 00:37:38,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ja osjeđam tu vojsku.

886
00:37:38,719 --> 00:37:41,260
[SPEAKER_00] Kako vidite suradnju sa vladom

887
00:37:41,260 --> 00:37:42,659
[SPEAKER_00] baš u području obrane

888
00:37:42,659 --> 00:37:43,780
[SPEAKER_00] nacionalne sigurnosti?

889
00:37:43,780 --> 00:37:45,699
[SPEAKER_00] Sigurno to ima prostora za nabraš?

890
00:37:45,699 --> 00:37:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naš je ustav takav kakav je.

891
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:50,840
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo parlamentarna demokracija,

892
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:52,360
[SPEAKER_01] a šefa države biramo izravno.

893
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:52,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam.

894
00:37:52,880 --> 00:37:56,780
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno se mora krenuti

895
00:37:56,780 --> 00:37:58,059
[SPEAKER_01] i definirati to ustav.

896
00:37:58,059 --> 00:38:00,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ili će se predsjednik birati

897
00:38:00,559 --> 00:38:01,440
[SPEAKER_01] iz parlamenta,

898
00:38:01,440 --> 00:38:02,840
[SPEAKER_01] biti protokolaran

899
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:05,559
[SPEAKER_01] i propisan nekakvim protokolarim,

900
00:38:05,559 --> 00:38:07,380
[SPEAKER_01] ili je velika težina

901
00:38:07,380 --> 00:38:08,099
[SPEAKER_01] izravnog izbora.

902
00:38:08,099 --> 00:38:09,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ne možemo mi osporiti

903
00:38:09,239 --> 00:38:10,760
[SPEAKER_01] da svi bivši predsjednici

904
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:12,179
[SPEAKER_01] Stipe Meš,

905
00:38:12,179 --> 00:38:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

906
00:38:12,500 --> 00:38:14,639
[SPEAKER_01] da to sem ponosan,

907
00:38:14,639 --> 00:38:15,380
[SPEAKER_01] to ću kasnije reći,

908
00:38:15,380 --> 00:38:16,139
[SPEAKER_01] ako Stipe Meš,

909
00:38:16,139 --> 00:38:16,840
[SPEAKER_01] ako mi citite.

910
00:38:16,840 --> 00:38:19,539
[SPEAKER_01] Jer bilo neke on za mene

911
00:38:19,539 --> 00:38:20,320
[SPEAKER_01] veli zajednik,

912
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:21,219
[SPEAKER_01] krivokletnik.

913
00:38:21,219 --> 00:38:22,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam na sudu s njime,

914
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:24,019
[SPEAKER_01] dobio sam ga na sudu.

915
00:38:24,019 --> 00:38:25,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam onaj ko me odruže ured,

916
00:38:25,800 --> 00:38:27,519
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam ponosan na to ured

917
00:38:27,519 --> 00:38:28,559
[SPEAKER_01] bivšeg predsjednika,

918
00:38:28,559 --> 00:38:29,940
[SPEAKER_01] to je bio moja man man,

919
00:38:29,940 --> 00:38:30,599
[SPEAKER_01] teka sam postao

920
00:38:30,599 --> 00:38:31,519
[SPEAKER_01] saborski zastupnik,

921
00:38:31,519 --> 00:38:32,460
[SPEAKER_01] prvi man man

922
00:38:32,460 --> 00:38:33,559
[SPEAKER_01] je bio

923
00:38:33,559 --> 00:38:34,940
[SPEAKER_01] ukidanje ureda

924
00:38:34,940 --> 00:38:35,699
[SPEAKER_01] bivšeg predsjednika

925
00:38:35,699 --> 00:38:36,440
[SPEAKER_01] Stipe Meš.

926
00:38:36,519 --> 00:38:38,980
[SPEAKER_01] i za mene,

927
00:38:38,980 --> 00:38:40,219
[SPEAKER_01] i na sudu sam ga povijedio,

928
00:38:40,219 --> 00:38:41,360
[SPEAKER_01] prosto u mene tuži

929
00:38:41,360 --> 00:38:41,679
[SPEAKER_01] i tako,

930
00:38:41,679 --> 00:38:41,900
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno,

931
00:38:41,900 --> 00:38:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] i proganja.

932
00:38:43,539 --> 00:38:44,059
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim,

933
00:38:44,059 --> 00:38:45,519
[SPEAKER_01] izravan izbor je tržina.

934
00:38:45,519 --> 00:38:48,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ne možemo mi to osporiti.

935
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:51,519
[SPEAKER_01] premijer sebira iz parlamenta.

936
00:38:51,519 --> 00:38:53,179
[SPEAKER_01] I tu je parlament

937
00:38:53,179 --> 00:38:54,179
[SPEAKER_01] obezvrjeđen,

938
00:38:54,179 --> 00:38:54,659
[SPEAKER_01] zato što

939
00:38:54,659 --> 00:38:56,159
[SPEAKER_01] za novi poslovnici,

940
00:38:56,159 --> 00:38:56,619
[SPEAKER_01] pravinci,

941
00:38:56,619 --> 00:38:57,920
[SPEAKER_01] za osnovno više nema debata,

942
00:38:57,920 --> 00:38:59,099
[SPEAKER_01] tri opamilizađe,

943
00:38:59,099 --> 00:39:00,619
[SPEAKER_01] da ćeš počneš govoriti

944
00:39:00,619 --> 00:39:01,280
[SPEAKER_01] svoj stav,

945
00:39:01,280 --> 00:39:02,179
[SPEAKER_01] već se van.

946
00:39:02,179 --> 00:39:03,460
[SPEAKER_01] Nema tu debate,

947
00:39:03,460 --> 00:39:04,920
[SPEAKER_01] nema parlamenta.

948
00:39:04,920 --> 00:39:06,340
[SPEAKER_01] I predsjednik,

949
00:39:06,340 --> 00:39:08,940
[SPEAKER_01] ili ćemo biti predsjednički,

950
00:39:08,940 --> 00:39:11,260
[SPEAKER_01] ili ćemo biti parlamentar.

951
00:39:11,260 --> 00:39:12,300
[SPEAKER_00] Kako mi se čini ta opcija,

952
00:39:12,300 --> 00:39:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] da se predsjednik...

953
00:39:13,539 --> 00:39:14,559
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ovo je nekakav hibrid,

954
00:39:14,559 --> 00:39:16,380
[SPEAKER_01] koji učito dobro ne funkcionira.

955
00:39:16,380 --> 00:39:19,300
[SPEAKER_01] Hibrid i predsjednik ima veliku težinu,

956
00:39:19,760 --> 00:39:22,920
[SPEAKER_01] kad bi ja bio pučki bravbran,

957
00:39:22,920 --> 00:39:24,900
[SPEAKER_01] te istinski bi se borio maksimalno,

958
00:39:24,900 --> 00:39:25,880
[SPEAKER_01] kao čovjek iz naroda.

959
00:39:25,880 --> 00:39:28,340
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, pitanje odgovornost.

960
00:39:28,340 --> 00:39:31,940
[SPEAKER_01] Koja je odgovornost predsjednika Republike?

961
00:39:31,940 --> 00:39:35,659
[SPEAKER_01] Njegove nadležnosti...

962
00:39:35,659 --> 00:39:38,480
[SPEAKER_01] Vrhovni zapovjednik

963
00:39:38,480 --> 00:39:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] su potpis službe,

964
00:39:41,539 --> 00:39:43,260
[SPEAKER_01] tu se brzo govorio iz Prijankovića,

965
00:39:43,260 --> 00:39:45,239
[SPEAKER_01] kad bio Plinca Cent nije spomenio,

966
00:39:45,239 --> 00:39:48,320
[SPEAKER_01] ne boj se o tome se dalo pričat.

967
00:39:48,940 --> 00:39:50,059
[SPEAKER_01] Znači i ovo ostalo,

968
00:39:50,059 --> 00:39:51,059
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, referendum,

969
00:39:51,059 --> 00:39:52,159
[SPEAKER_01] mogućnost da pokrene,

970
00:39:52,159 --> 00:39:53,280
[SPEAKER_01] ali opet su potpulade.

971
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:54,900
[SPEAKER_01] Znači nema nekakve

972
00:39:54,900 --> 00:39:58,139
[SPEAKER_01] težine iz izravnog izbora.

973
00:39:58,139 --> 00:40:01,159
[SPEAKER_01] Pa su Hrvati birali izravno.

974
00:40:01,159 --> 00:40:02,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ko se koliko nira za predsjednika,

975
00:40:02,440 --> 00:40:03,519
[SPEAKER_01] ko dobije, to je veliko...

976
00:40:03,519 --> 00:40:04,619
[SPEAKER_01] Bez obzira šta misli o kojem.

977
00:40:05,019 --> 00:40:06,820
[SPEAKER_01] E, sad toga svega,

978
00:40:06,820 --> 00:40:08,940
[SPEAKER_01] kako pronaći model?

979
00:40:08,940 --> 00:40:11,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ustav je takav kakav je.

980
00:40:11,320 --> 00:40:13,780
[SPEAKER_01] Franje Tužman je bio poluponov,

981
00:40:13,780 --> 00:40:14,860
[SPEAKER_01] više predsjednički.

982
00:40:14,860 --> 00:40:16,480
[SPEAKER_01] Stipe meše,

983
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:17,619
[SPEAKER_01] to se redukulizira,

984
00:40:17,619 --> 00:40:18,920
[SPEAKER_01] inače i je redukul,

985
00:40:18,920 --> 00:40:21,599
[SPEAKER_01] jer je obziradio sve vrijednosti

986
00:40:21,599 --> 00:40:23,340
[SPEAKER_01] koje su stečene

987
00:40:23,340 --> 00:40:24,360
[SPEAKER_01] u Domovinskom eratu

988
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:26,199
[SPEAKER_01] kao temelju državne države.

989
00:40:26,360 --> 00:40:29,059
[SPEAKER_01] Zoranje je teška.

990
00:40:29,059 --> 00:40:32,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bi osobno

991
00:40:32,159 --> 00:40:33,780
[SPEAKER_01] odmah sazvao

992
00:40:33,780 --> 00:40:35,019
[SPEAKER_01] svjednicu

993
00:40:35,019 --> 00:40:37,440
[SPEAKER_01] po Ustavu,

994
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:38,579
[SPEAKER_01] što može presnikam.

995
00:40:38,579 --> 00:40:40,659
[SPEAKER_01] Nema glasov, nema ruku,

996
00:40:40,659 --> 00:40:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] nema to što je stranom vlade.

997
00:40:42,039 --> 00:40:45,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ponudio bi demokratske mjere

998
00:40:45,840 --> 00:40:46,960
[SPEAKER_01] odmah.

999
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:48,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ne ponudio mjere,

1000
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:49,599
[SPEAKER_01] nego mjere koje sam provodio,

1001
00:40:49,599 --> 00:40:51,000
