1007
00:40:58,840 --> 00:40:59,199
[SPEAKER_01] nikom.

1008
00:40:59,199 --> 00:41:01,360
[SPEAKER_01] I to je legitivno njivo pravo.

1009
00:41:01,360 --> 00:41:03,219
