1025
00:41:28,719 --> 00:41:30,699
[SPEAKER_01] ne snalaze se najbude.

1026
00:41:30,699 --> 00:41:32,800
[SPEAKER_01] I još i koriste,

1027
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:33,860
[SPEAKER_01] ko zna na koji način,

1028
00:41:33,860 --> 00:41:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] da li plaćaju,

1029
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:35,579
