[SPEAKER_01] uvozi razne snage,

1045
00:42:01,519 --> 00:42:02,920
[SPEAKER_01] te dovodeo smo njenja cijene

1046
00:42:02,920 --> 00:42:04,639
[SPEAKER_01] i daljnjeg iseljavanja

1047
00:42:04,639 --> 00:42:05,380
[SPEAKER_01] naših ljudi,

1048
00:42:05,380 --> 00:42:06,440
[SPEAKER_01] to je činjenica.

1049
00:42:07,199 --> 00:42:08,420
[SPEAKER_01] i to je isto jedan

1050
00:42:08,420 --> 00:42:09,059
