1074
00:42:36,980 --> 00:42:37,840
[SPEAKER_00] zadržati ovlast

1075
00:42:37,840 --> 00:42:39,460
[SPEAKER_00] imenovanja i razriješenja

1076
00:42:39,460 --> 00:42:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] načelnika glavnog stoža

1077
00:42:40,619 --> 00:42:41,420
