1087
00:42:54,699 --> 00:42:55,960
[SPEAKER_01] prvog načelnika

1088
00:42:55,960 --> 00:42:58,320
[SPEAKER_01] je katastrofana,

1089
00:42:58,320 --> 00:43:01,079
[SPEAKER_01] jer ipak,

1090
00:43:01,079 --> 00:43:02,199
